The '''Battle Group of [[Yun-Txiin]]''' was one of the five battle groups the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] used during the [[Battle of Ebaq]] 9.

==History==
When the fleet arrived, the group worked with the [[Battle Group of Yun-Q'aah|Battle Group]] of [[Yun-Q'aah]] to flank [[General/Legends|General]] [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander's]] squadron. However, as the battle progressed, the numbers took their toll on the Yun-Txiin battle group. When [[Warmaster]] [[Tsavong Lah]] ordered the fleet to withdraw, the Yun-Txiin group and the [[Battle Group of Yun-Harla|Battle Group]] of [[Yun-Harla]] were the first to withdraw. However, they were also the first to encounter the minefield the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] had set up. The Battle Group of Yun-Txiin, already overtaxed due to the fighting at [[Ebaq 9]], took massive casualties in the minefield.

